message: Hi Bob, I propose that I take $60 and you take $40. This seems like a fair starting point for me, considering I initiated the proposal. Let me know what you think!

Hi Alice, I propose that I receive $52.63 and you receive $47.37. If we delay further, the total value drops even more. I believe this split reflects our future bargaining positions, ensuring that you get as much as you would expect by waiting. What do you think?
